1955;;The Naked Dawn;;American;;Edgar G. Ulmer;;Arthur Kennedy, Betta St. John;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Naked_Dawn;;The story focuses on a poor but proud farmer named Manuel and his wife Maria. When glib-tongued drifter Santiago tries to get Manuel mixed up in a robbery, the farmer is at first resistant, but is goaded into joining Santiago. Corrupted by the prospect of untold wealth, Manuel begins plotting the murder of Santiago; meanwhile, Maria makes plans to run off with the handsome stranger.